{"tid":101861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"痴線，咁都有","createTime":"2017-01-31T08:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T09:52:56.000Z","uid":33465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"742cb509f1eb0c0147684ced55d994e1b5b0848c","tid":101861,"uid":33465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T08:14:33.000Z","msg":"坐喺港鐵到，個大肚婆一上車就摸住嗰肚。咁好啦，我讓比佢，佢比佢嗰唔知係家姐定friend坐，跟住又摸嗰肚等我隔離個賓賓又讓比佢。老馮咁。香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87b0a7dbb82d314a46633ba7a6bac7e1dcf86dbf","tid":101861,"uid":22046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:47:50.000Z","msg":"所以我唔會主動讓<br />\n前兩日有個大肚婆 拖住個細路<br />\n個細路話好攰 我打死都唔主動讓比個大肚婆<br />\n肯定係比條o靚仔坐左<br />\n<br />\n除非個大肚婆問/好明顯想坐<br />\n我就會講到明比大肚婆坐唔比其他人坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主個case 根本仆街<br />\n大肚婆要坐就自己親戚讓<br />\n仲要人比多個位佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32a0eabd2a5a1e2730bd9f25daa6145699816cd6","tid":101861,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"咁撚無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}